    {
      "id": "box1A_content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 55,
      "y": 162,
      "width": 690,
      "height": 405,
      "text": "1. withAuth + withUsageCheck middleware\n2. Fetch User + LearnerModel + top 10 ErrorPatterns\n3. Extract: targetLang, nativeLang, cefrGrammar, cefrFluency\n\n4. Parallel curriculum queries:\n   ├─ getVocabTargets(userId, lang, cefr, 5)\n   │   in-progress items first, then new at CEFR+1 level\n   ├─ getNextGrammarFocus(userId, lang, cefr)\n   │   first uncovered pattern at current+next level\n   ├─ getGrammarStructuresInScope(lang, cefr)\n   │   all patterns A1..current level (max 15 for agent)\n   └─ searchMemories(userId, sessionFocus, 10)\n       recent memories grouped by type\n\n5. Top 3 error patterns selected for review\n6. selectNextDomain() → cycles 10 domains (food, travel, work...)\n7. Build lessonPlan + systemPrompt (no LLM call needed)\n\n8. Parallel writes:\n   ├─ prisma.lesson.create(goal, plan, systemPrompt)\n   ├─ user.totalLessons++\n   └─ getUsageInfo() → remainingSeconds\n\n→ Returns { sessionId, plan, agentMetadata, remainingSeconds }",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "groupIds": [],
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. withAuth + withUsageCheck middleware\n2. Fetch User + LearnerModel + top 10 ErrorPatterns\n3. Extract: targetLang, nativeLang, cefrGrammar, cefrFluency\n\n4. Parallel curriculum queries:\n   ├─ getVocabTargets(userId, lang, cefr, 5)\n   │   in-progress items first, then new at CEFR+1 level\n   ├─ getNextGrammarFocus(userId, lang, cefr)\n   │   first uncovered pattern at current+next level\n   ├─ getGrammarStructuresInScope(lang, cefr)\n   │   all patterns A1..current level (max 15 for agent)\n   └─ searchMemories(userId, sessionFocus, 10)\n       recent memories grouped by type\n\n5. Top 3 error patterns selected for review\n6. selectNextDomain() → cycles 10 domains (food, travel, work...)\n7. Build lessonPlan + systemPrompt (no LLM call needed)\n\n8. Parallel writes:\n   ├─ prisma.lesson.create(goal, plan, systemPrompt)\n   ├─ user.totalLessons++\n   └─ getUsageInfo() → remainingSeconds\n\n→ Returns { sessionId, plan, agentMetadata, remainingSeconds }",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 2006,
      "index": "a6",
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "seed": 1006,
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "updated": 1742400000000
