    {
      "id": "box2A_content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 55,
      "y": 692,
      "width": 375,
      "height": 146,
      "text": "POST /voice/livekit-token\n1. deleteRoom(lingle-{userId}) — clean stale\n2. createRoom(nodeId, emptyTimeout=300s)\n3. JWT token (join + publish + subscribe)\n→ Returns { token, url, roomName }\n\nBrowser:\n  room.connect(url, token)\n  setMicrophoneEnabled(true)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "groupIds": [],
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "POST /voice/livekit-token\n1. deleteRoom(lingle-{userId}) — clean stale\n2. createRoom(nodeId, emptyTimeout=300s)\n3. JWT token (join + publish + subscribe)\n→ Returns { token, url, roomName }\n\nBrowser:\n  room.connect(url, token)\n  setMicrophoneEnabled(true)",
