      "width": 375,
      "height": 146,
      "text": "POST /voice/start-agent\n1. Validate room = lingle-{userId}\n2. Delete stale dispatches\n3. createDispatch(roomName,\n     'lingle-agent',\n     metadata = JSON.stringify(agentMetadata))\n\nAgent receives dispatch →\n  parses AgentMetadata from room metadata",
