    {
      "id": "box2C_content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 55,
      "y": 902,
      "width": 1210,
      "height": 146,
      "text": "1. System prompt (4 slots, ~1800 tokens total):\n   Slot 1: Persona + behavioral rules (~800 tok) | Slot 2: Learner profile + CEFR + errors (~500 tok)\n   Slot 3: Session plan + vocab/grammar targets (~200 tok) | Slot 4: Episodic memories (~300 tok)\n2. Tools: 8 base (logError, noteStrength, saveMemory, queueCorrection, adjustDifficulty, updatePhase, setVocab, endLesson) + 3 onboarding\n3. Pipeline: Silero VAD → Soniox STT (realtime WS, 24kHz) → Claude Sonnet (streaming, 200 max tok) → Cartesia TTS (persistent WS)\n4. Redis session state: createDefaultSessionState() — TTL 4h, phase=warmup, difficulty=2, empty tracking arrays",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "groupIds": [],
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. System prompt (4 slots, ~1800 tokens total):\n   Slot 1: Persona + behavioral rules (~800 tok) | Slot 2: Learner profile + CEFR + errors (~500 tok)\n   Slot 3: Session plan + vocab/grammar targets (~200 tok) | Slot 4: Episodic memories (~300 tok)\n2. Tools: 8 base (logError, noteStrength, saveMemory, queueCorrection, adjustDifficulty, updatePhase, setVocab, endLesson) + 3 onboarding\n3. Pipeline: Silero VAD → Soniox STT (realtime WS, 24kHz) → Claude Sonnet (streaming, 200 max tok) → Cartesia TTS (persistent WS)\n4. Redis session state: createDefaultSessionState() — TTL 4h, phase=warmup, difficulty=2, empty tracking arrays",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 2020,
      "index": "c0",
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
