    {
      "id": "box3B_content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 55,
      "y": 1462,
      "width": 530,
      "height": 195,
      "text": "1. Skip garbage transcripts (noise, too short)\n2. Read session state from Redis\n3. serializeForPrompt(state) → inject into Slot 3:\n   phase, elapsed time, difficulty level,\n   recent errors (last 5), repeated patterns,\n   operational difficulty constraints\n4. Context compression (if > 20 turn pairs):\n   Keep 12 recent turns in full\n   Haiku summarizes older turns (2-3 sentences)\n5. Prompt caching strategy:\n   System prompt: cached (ephemeral)\n   Turns 1..N-1: cached at 2nd-to-last user msg\n   Only newest turn uncached (~85-90% savings)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "groupIds": [],
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Skip garbage transcripts (noise, too short)\n2. Read session state from Redis\n3. serializeForPrompt(state) → inject into Slot 3:\n   phase, elapsed time, difficulty level,\n   recent errors (last 5), repeated patterns,\n   operational difficulty constraints\n4. Context compression (if > 20 turn pairs):\n   Keep 12 recent turns in full\n   Haiku summarizes older turns (2-3 sentences)\n5. Prompt caching strategy:\n   System prompt: cached (ephemeral)\n   Turns 1..N-1: cached at 2nd-to-last user msg\n   Only newest turn uncached (~85-90% savings)",
