    {
      "id": "box4A_content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 55,
      "y": 1792,
      "width": 670,
      "height": 486,
      "text": "1. Fetch lesson from DB + read Redis session state\n2. duration = now - lesson.startedAt\n\n3. Parallel analysis:\n   ├─ generateTitle() — Claude Haiku\n   │   \"3-7 word English title for: {goal}\"\n   ├─ updateCefrScores() — Claude Haiku\n   │   Input: current scores, errors by type,\n   │     strengths noted, avg latency, difficulty\n   │   Output: grammarDelta, fluencyDelta (±0.3 max)\n   │   Rules: ±0.05-0.1 typical, ±0.2+ exceptional\n   │   Clamp: force min ±0.05, range [1.0, 6.0]\n   └─ updateErrorPatterns()\n       Per rule: prisma.errorPattern.upsert\n       occurrenceCount++, sessionsSeen.push(id)\n\n4. Bulk write: errorLog.createMany(errorsLogged[])\n\n5. Generate corrections doc from corrections[]\n\n6. Parallel DB writes:\n   ├─ lesson.update(endedAt, duration, summary,\n   │   errorsCount, topics[], vocab[], corrections)\n   ├─ dailyUsage.upsert(+= conversationSeconds)\n   └─ user.update(totalMinutes += durationMinutes)\n\n7. Fire-and-forget:\n   ├─ addMemories(userId, sessionState)\n   │   → persist memoriesQueued + LLM-extract facts\n   └─ runLongitudinalAnalysis() (from session 3+)\n       errorDensity = errors / (~15 words/min)\n       Haiku → speechProfile, priorityFocus,\n       errorDensityTrend (improving|stable|declining)\n\n8. DELETE session:{sessionId} from Redis\n\n→ Returns { cefrDelta, errorsCount, correctionsDoc }",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "groupIds": [],
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Fetch lesson from DB + read Redis session state\n2. duration = now - lesson.startedAt\n\n3. Parallel analysis:\n   ├─ generateTitle() — Claude Haiku\n   │   \"3-7 word English title for: {goal}\"\n   ├─ updateCefrScores() — Claude Haiku\n   │   Input: current scores, errors by type,\n   │     strengths noted, avg latency, difficulty\n   │   Output: grammarDelta, fluencyDelta (±0.3 max)\n   │   Rules: ±0.05-0.1 typical, ±0.2+ exceptional\n   │   Clamp: force min ±0.05, range [1.0, 6.0]\n   └─ updateErrorPatterns()\n       Per rule: prisma.errorPattern.upsert\n       occurrenceCount++, sessionsSeen.push(id)\n\n4. Bulk write: errorLog.createMany(errorsLogged[])\n\n5. Generate corrections doc from corrections[]\n\n6. Parallel DB writes:\n   ├─ lesson.update(endedAt, duration, summary,\n   │   errorsCount, topics[], vocab[], corrections)\n   ├─ dailyUsage.upsert(+= conversationSeconds)\n   └─ user.update(totalMinutes += durationMinutes)\n\n7. Fire-and-forget:\n   ├─ addMemories(userId, sessionState)\n   │   → persist memoriesQueued + LLM-extract facts\n   └─ runLongitudinalAnalysis() (from session 3+)\n       errorDensity = errors / (~15 words/min)\n       Haiku → speechProfile, priorityFocus,\n       errorDensityTrend (improving|stable|declining)\n\n8. DELETE session:{sessionId} from Redis\n\n→ Returns { cefrDelta, errorsCount, correctionsDoc }",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 2036,
      "index": "d6",
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "seed": 1036,
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "updated": 1742400000000
    },
