    {
      "id": "box4B_content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 785,
      "y": 1792,
      "width": 330.46875,
      "height": 550.8000000000001,
      "text": "Lesson:\n  endedAt, durationMinutes\n  summary (generated title)\n  errorsCount, topicsCovered[]\n  vocabIntroduced[], phasesCompleted[]\n  difficultyFinal, correctionsDoc\n\nLearnerModel:\n  cefrGrammar += delta (clamped 1.0-6.0)\n  cefrFluency += delta (clamped 1.0-6.0)\n  sessionsCompleted++\n  avgResponseLatencySec (updated)\n  speechProfile (from longitudinal analysis)\n  priorityFocus (single most important area)\n  errorDensityTrend: improving|stable|declining\n  errorDensityPer100Words (computed)\n\nErrorPattern (per rule — upsert):\n  occurrenceCount += N\n  lastSeenAt = now\n  sessionsSeen.push(lessonId)\n\nErrorLog (bulk insert):\n  One row per error logged during session\n  errorType, phrase, correction, rule\n\nMemory (from memoriesQueued):\n  content, memoryType, source='conversation'\n  Deduplicated by first 50 chars\n\nDailyUsage: conversationSeconds += duration\nUser: totalMinutes += durationMinutes\n\nREDIS: DELETE session:{sessionId}",
